{"tid":692212,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔小心同女朋友扑野叫左佢龜蜜個名","createTime":"2018-06-06T12:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T08:08:16.000Z","uid":59569,"like":3,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"039d94c07963cf1d22c4015293e08f5f529eff9f","tid":692212,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:22:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今朝起身見咁撚大雨<br />\n緊係留喺安全既地方先喇<br />\n起左身冇耐就收到女朋友同我講早晨<br />\n問佢今日有咩做<br />\n佢話好大雨但又肚餓喎<br />\n<br />\n作為人地男朋友就盡下責任<br />\n同佢相隔都係幾個地鐵站咁<br />\n我就拿拿林買野食上去<br />\n上到去之後點知仲大風大雨屌<br />\n心諗點撚樣走呢<br />\nuncle 同 auntie 都返左工<br />\n得返我同佢喺間屋都on99<br />\n一時諗唔到有咩做唯有扑野hea下時間<br />\n<br />\n我地係唔用套既<br />\n次次都係拎出黎射<br />\n佢今日問我想射落佢邊個位<br />\n我就講「射lin喇」<br />\n點知我一時醒唔起佢有個龜蜜又係呢個柒下柒下既名<br />\n女朋友聽完之後即刻黑撚晒面<br />\n問我做咩無啦啦提呢個名<br />\n之後一直俾佢屌到停雨<br />\n仆街，下次我直接塞我碌鳩隊埋落你個口度咪撚嘈"},{"pid":"fa1b0a25de3970bcf06bbd9d1457923d3452b61c","tid":692212,"uid":76697,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:23:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a080bdf98b742da672582248816935afd281b483","tid":692212,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"fa1b0a25de3970bcf06bbd9d1457923d3452b61c","tid":692212,"uid":76697,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:23:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" />"},{"pid":"69417dc5300018b8bc29a040781df42b31876231","tid":692212,"uid":183338,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"乜撚野龜蜜？？"},{"pid":"27e8d424b1982c196d072624d72901993d30eb9e","tid":692212,"uid":33875,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/202730_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F202730_d0